2. The end and purpose of this
booke, is to prooue that Position.
3. This cannot be beleeued, but by
the helpe of prayer. 4. It cannot
be proued <HI>A Priorj.</HI> 5. Yet may it
be shewed <HI>A Posteriorj.</HI> pag. 1.</ITEM>
</LIST>
