<ITEM>That there is not any
<HI>Nation,</HI> but it hath his Religion.
1. Ancient histories insinuate it.
2. New histories affirme it. 3. Tra|uellers
confirme it. 4. A generall
surueigh of their gods declareth it.
5. A particular surueigh of their
