of the same Spirit. <HI>Compara species Apostoli, &amp; Isaiae: Alij (inquit) datur, per
Spiritum, sermo s<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">entie: statim &amp; Es<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">as, Spiritum s<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">entiae p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">suit. Alij, sermo
