the Apostle<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> place with Isaies. To one</HI> (saith the Apostle) <HI>is giu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">n by the Spi|rit,
<PB N="197" REF="104">
the word o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> wisedome: the Spirit</HI> (saith the Prophet) <HI>is the spirit of wisedom.
To another</HI> (saith the Apostle) <HI>is giuen the word of knowledge: the spirit</HI> (saith
