Apostle) <HI>is giuen fa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">th, by the same spirit: the spirit</HI> (saith the Prophet) <HI>is the
spirit of Religion, an<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> of the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> of God. To another</HI> (saith the Apostle) <HI>is gi|uen
